  "description": "These low-prep, bean-packed cheesy melts take the hassle out of quesadillas! You'll mash kidney beans with mature cheddar and punchy chipotle paste for warmth, before piling the mix into soft tortillas and simply baking in the oven for moreishly melty, fully loaded veggie wraps. Say cheese!\r\n ",
